    <stitle>3300 HOOD, GRILLE, FENDERS AND BUMPER - Description - FENDER EXTENSIONS</stitle>
    <svcsection/>
    <svcproc svcproctype="describe" graphiccount="1">
        <title>FENDER EXTENSIONS</title>
        <para>Fender extensions (
            <hotlnk xrefid="f0901009">Figure 9</hotlnk>) are an integral part of the fender system on the 3300 series
            bus chassis. The fender extensions have been designed to provide splash and spray protection. This protects
            the lower front of the cowl from splash and road debris kicked up by the front tires.
        </para>
        <figure id="f0901009" figsize="col-wide">
            <graphic filename="../figg09/G0901009.webp" type="webp" scalefit="1" scalefitwidth="272px"
                     scalefitheight="312px"/>
            <caption>Figure 9. 3300 Series Fender Extension (Driver Side Shown)</caption>
